{"tid":1321474,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好信散仔割蓆之類嘅消息","createTime":"2019-07-15T16:25:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T04:13:31.000Z","uid":273617,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"776fd7f6223e2c5f10eb84f1b7c70d85f5c58b75","tid":1321474,"uid":273617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:25:23.000Z","msg":"屌，你割蓆又唔辭工，下次咪一樣打鳩手足，仲有被捕手足一個都未放，依家只有敵我之分，差佬作為敵方割春袋都唔撚關我事啦onlun79<br />\n<br />\n佢依家割蓆原因只有一個，就係我地<strong>行動升級</strong>啦，散仔係人數劣勢下真係怕俾人熔左<br />\n<br />\n依家更加證明有效做法得一條路，只要被攻擊就要升級，對所有冒警恐怖分子毫不留情攻擊，令佢失去攻擊市民嘅能力<br />\n<br />\n仲有，見到柏林sir記住要好好同佢傾下計，手足條數要慢慢deal好佢架，係咪？"},{"pid":"ed67b5214ac99611b8e296a1d8818ea812cc8219","tid":1321474,"uid":273617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:33:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb28b62a4298c306e4a615bd7d5459159b0fc34e","tid":1321474,"uid":273617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:37:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"72ef2f3a8fff1695299844e1faad7fbbc02fc441","tid":1321474,"uid":273617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:47:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1df70412813e9fa45e4d2335c846b26bbfb875a3","tid":1321474,"uid":273617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:13:31.000Z","msg":"推"}]}